cal rarity, and the high deforestation rates in their distributional area, we suggest that these three species must be considered as taxa threatened with extinction.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Morales-Mart\u00ednez, Darwin M", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rodr\u00edguez-Posada, Miguel E", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ram\u00edrez-Chaves, H\u00e9ctor E", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ortega, Jorge", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ed7bc23f16b63fea3bfc45a1a8050195", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/99c394c45a193f1138b705ef03c5a2dde094976cbd75ab5e7e800aa71558cb3f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/IN8PB7AU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/IN8PB7AU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/028966b5c5867a564e29fa2d20f4f7b4!/b293220-295707", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "90-100", "title": "Journal of Mammalogy", "volume": "102"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ed7bc23f16b63fea3bfc45a1a8050195"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:IN8PB7AU"}, {"identifier": "10.1093/jmammal/gyaa137"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relatio